<div class="min-vh-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center px-4 px-lg-5 banner">
  <h1 class="m-0">Hello World!</h1>
  <h1 class="mb-4">I'm Fairul Izwan | Software Engineer</h1>
  <ul class="p-0 mb-4">
    <li><i class="fa-brands fa-2xl fa-square-github"></i></li>
    <li><i class="fa-brands fa-2xl fa-linkedin"></i></li>
    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-2xl fa-envelope"></i></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="row">
    <p class="col-12 col-lg-6">I love exploring and creating 🚀 I'm a lifelong learner 🎓 and I might have a thing for traditional Neapolitan Pizza 🍕</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container px-4 px-lg-0 py-5 m-auto">

  <div class="home-skills mb-5">
    <h2>My Skills</h2>
    <div class="row shadow rounded border p-2 py-3 skills-card">
      <div class="skills-img col-12 col-lg-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
        <%= image_tag "fairul.jpeg", class: "rounded" %>
      </div>
      <div class="skills-con col-12 col-lg-9 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
        <ul class="p-0 m-0 mb-3 justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
          <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
          <li>Ruby</li>
          <li>SQL</li>
          <li>Javascript</li>
          <li>Stimulus</li>
          <li>HTML</li>
          <li>CSS</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>An inspiring Software Developer</h4>
        <p>Summary about self here *Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quia consequatur harum perspiciatis maxime at perferendis temporibus modi asperiores repudiandae. Sit adipisci optio ducimus expedita ad quam hic nisi veritatis vitae?*</p>
        <p>Read more *scroll bar*</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <div class="home-project row">
        <div class="project-content pe-5 col-12 col-lg-9 order-2 order-lg-1">
          <h4 class="m-0"><%= project.role %></h4>
          <h3><%= project.name %></h3>
          <ul class="m-0 p-0 my-4">
            <% project.languages.each do |l| %>
              <li><%= l.name %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
          <p class ="mb-5"><%= project.summary %></p>
          <%= link_to "View Project", project_path(project), class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>
        <div class="project-img col-10 m-auto col-lg-3 order-1 order-lg-2">
          <%= image_tag "fairul.jpeg", class: "mb-3 rounded w-100" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <h3>Open to work, let's have a chat</h3>
  <p>*Email Address*</p>

  <p>render footer</p>
</div>
